      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, but it feels a little bit like a generic template. Can you make it a bit more powerful? Like, maybe touch on why it's actually important for a business like ours to do this, instead of just saying we're doing it. Make it sound like it's a really necessary and foundational thing for the brand's values.",
